data.description: Renovated in 2014 with newer plumbing and electric, this expanded Oak Park foursquare presents a host of features. The enclosed front porch serves as a haven from the elements before stepping into the heart of the home. Stepping through the front door, notice the newly refinished hardwood floors and fresh paint throughout. The first floor boasts an expanded living room, formal dining room, powder room, and an eat-in kitchen with room for a banquet or built-ins. Pull up a stool at the island and savor the updated kitchen featuring stone counters, stainless steel appliances, light cabinetry, and a pantry. The enclosed back porch functions as an ideal mudroom, offering a landing space at the end of the day. The backyard provides ample greenspace and leads to a 2-car garage. Upstairs, discover three bedrooms with hardwood floors in two, including the primary, and new carpet in the third. The brand-new remodeled second-floor bathroom showcases a stunning tiled shower and floor, along with a new vanity. The finished basement offers an additional bedroom and a full second bath, creating a perfect guest arrangement. A basement family room and laundry room, complete with two sump pumps (one with a new battery back-up), round out the lower level. Enjoy the desirable north Oak Park location within the Hatch Elementary district, with incredible neighbors, block parties, and convenient access to North Ave.
